(ijs mnu`K dy) mn ivc sdw-iQr rihx vwlw pRBU (v`sdw hY), (jo) mUMhoN (BI) ausy pRBU nUM (jpdw hY),
(jo mnu`K) iek Akwl purK qoN ibnw (ikqy BI) iksy hor nUM nhIN vyKdw,
hy nwnk! (auh mnu`K) iehnW guxW dy kwrx bRhmigAwnI ho jWdw hY ]1]
