bRhmigAwnI (mnu`K ivkwrW vloN) sdw-bydwZ (rihMdy hn)
ijvyN pwxI ivc (au~gy hoey) kaul Pu`l (ic`kV qoN) sw& huMdy hn[
bRhmigAwnI (mnu`K) (swry pwpW nUM swV dyNdy hn) pwpW qoN bcy rihMdy hn,
ijvyN sUrj swry (rsW) nUM sukw dyNdw hY[
bRhmigAwnI dy AMdr (sB vl) ieko ijhI nzr (nwl q`kx dw suBwau huMdw) hY,
ijvyN hvw rwjy qy kMgwl nUM ieko ijhI l`gdI hY[
(koeI Blw khy BwvyN burw, pr) bRhmigAwnI mnu`KW dy AMdr iek-qwr hOslw (kwiem rihMdw) hY,
ijvyN DrqI nUM koeI qW Koqrdw hY, qy koeI cMdn dy lypx krdw hY (pr DrqI nUM prvwh nhIN)[
bRhmigAwnI mnu`KW dw (BI) iehI gux hY,
hy nwnk! ijvyN A`g dw kudrqI suBwau hY (hryk cIz dI mYl swV dyxI) ]1]
bRhmigAwnI mnu`K (ivkwrW dI mYl qoN sdw bicAw rih ky) mhw inrml hY,
ijvyN pwxI nUM kdy mYl nhIN rih skdI (bu^wrwq Awidk bx ky muV sw& dw sw&[)
bRhmigAwnI dy mn ivc (ieh) cwnx ho jWdw hY (ik pRBU hr QW mOjUd hY)
ijvyN DrqI auqy AwkwS (sB QW ivAwpk hY[)
bRhmigAwnI nUM s`jx qy vYrI ieko ijhw hY,
(ikauNk) aus dy AMdr AhMkwr nhIN hY (iksy dy cMgy mMdy slUk dw hrK sog nhIN)[
bRhmigAwnI (Awqmk AvsQw ivc) sB qoN au~cw hY,
(pr) Awpxy mn ivc (Awpxy Awp nUM) sB qoN nIvW (jwxdw hY)[
auhI mnu`K bRhmigAwnI bxdy hn,
hy nwnk! ijn@W nUM pRBU Awp bxwauNdw hY ]2]
bRhmigAwnI swry (bMidAW) dy pYrW dI ^wk (ho ky rihMdw) hY;
bRhmigAwnI ny Awqmk AwnMd nUM pCwx ilAw hY[
bRhmigAwnI dI sB auqy ^uSI huMdI hY (Bwv, bRhm-igAwnI sB nwl h`sdy-m`Qy rihMdw hY)
Aqy auh koeI mMdw kMm nhIN krdw[
bRhmigAwnI sdw sB vl ieko ijhI nzr nwl q`kdw hY,
aus dI nzr qoN (sB auqy) AMimRq dI vrKw huMdI hY[
bRhmigAwnI (mwieAw dy) bMDnW qoN Awzwd huMdw hY,
Aqy aus dI jIvn-jugqI ivkwrW qoN rihq hY[
(r`bI-) igAwn bRhmigAwnI dI ^urwk hY (Bwv, bRhmigAwnI dI Awqmk izMdgI dw Awsrw hY),
hy nwnk! bRhmigAwnI dI surq Akwl purK nwl juVI rihMdI hY ]3]
bRhmigAwnI iek Akwl purK auqy Aws r`Kdw hY;
bRhmigAwnI (dI au~cI Awqmk AvsQw) dw kdy nws nhIN huMdw[
bRhmigAwnI dy ihrdy ivc grIbI itkI rihMdI hY,
Aqy aus nUM dUijAW dI BlweI krn dw (sdw) cwau (cVRihAw rihMdw) hY[
bRhmigAwnI dy mn ivc (mwieAw dw) jMjwl nhIN ivAwpdw,
(ikauNik) auh Btkdy mn nUM kwbU kr ky (mwieAw vloN) rok skdw hY[
jo kuJ (pRBU vloN) huMdw hY, bRhmigAwnI nUM Awpxy mn ivc Blw pRqIq huMdw hY,
ies qrHW) aus dw mnu`Kw jnm cMgI qrHW kwmXwb huMdw hY[
bRhmigAwnI dI sMgq ivc sB dw byVw pwr huMdw hY,
(ikauNik) hy nwnk! bRhmigAwnI dI rwhIN swrw jgq (hI) (pRBU dw nwm) jpx l`g pYNdw hY ]4]
bRhmigAwnI dy ihrdy ivc (sdw) iek Akwl purK dw ipAwr (v`sdw hY),
(qwhIeyN) pRBU bRhmigAwnI dy AMg-sMg rihMdw hY[
bRhmigAwnI dy mn ivc (pRBU dw) nwm (hI) tyk hY,
Aqy nwm hI aus dw prvwr hY[
bRhmigAwnI sdw (ivkwrW dy hmly vloN) sucyq rihMdw hY,
Aqy 'mYN mYN' krn vwlI m`q C`f dyNdw hY[
bRhmigAwnI dy mn ivc au~cy suK dw mwlk Akwl purK v`sdw hY,
(qwhIeyN) aus dy ihrdy-rUp Gr ivc sdw ^uSI iKVwE hY[
bRhmigAwnI (mnu`K) suK qy SWqI ivc itikAw rihMdw hY;
(qy) hy nwnk! bRhmigAwnI (dI ies au~cI Awqmk AvsQw) dw kdy nws nhIN huMdw ]5]
bRhmigAwnI (mnu`K) Akwl purK dw mhrm bx jWdw hY,
Aqy auh iek pRBU nwl hI ipAwr krdw hY[
bRhmigAwnI dy mn ivc (sdw) byi&krI rihMdI hY,
aus dw aupdyS (BI hornW nUM) pivqR krn vwlw huMdw hY[
(auhI mnu`K bRhmigAwnI bxdw hY) ijs nUM pRBU Awp bxwauNdw hY,
bRhmigAwnI dw bVw nwmxw ho jWdw hY[
bRhmigAwnI dw dIdwr v`fy BwgW nwl pweIdw hY;
bRhmigAwnI qoN sdw sdky jweIey[
iSv (Awidk dyvqy BI) bRhmigAwnI nUM Bwldy iPrdy hn;
hy nwnk! Akwl purK Awp bRhmigAwnI (dw rUp) hY ]6]
bRhmigAwnI (dy guxW) dw mu`l nhIN pY skdw,
swry hI (gux) bRhmigAwnI dy AMdr hn[
kyhVw mnu`K bRhmigAwnI (dI au~cI izMdgI) dw Byq pw skdw hY?
bRhmigAwnI dy A`gy sdw inaUxw hI (P`bdw) hY[
bRhmigAwnI (dI mihmw) dw A`Dw A`Kr BI nhIN ikhw jw skdw;
bRhmigAwnI swry (jIvW) dw pUjRX hY[
bRhmigAwnI (dI au~cI izMdgI) dw AMdwzw kOx lw skdw hY?
aus dI hwlq (aus vrgw) bRhmigAwnI hI jwxdw hY[
bRhmigAwnI (dy guxW dy smuMdr) dw koeI h`d bMnw nhIN;
hy nwnk! sdw bRhmigAwnI dy crnW qy ipAw rhu ]7]
bRhmigAwnI swry jgq dw bxwaux vwlw hY,
sdw hI ijaUNdw hY, kdy (jnm) mrn dy gyV ivc nhIN AwauNdw[
bRhmigAwnI mukqI dw rwh (d`sx vwlw qy au~cI Awqmk) izMdgI dw dyx vwlw hY,
auhI pUrn purK qy kwdr hY[
bRhmigAwnI in^simAW dw ^sm hY,
sB dI shwieqw krdw hY[
swrw id`sdw jgq bRhmigAwnI dw (Awpxw) hY,
auh (qW pRq`K) Awp hI r`b hY[
bRhmigAwnI dI mihmw (koeI) bRhmigAwnI hI kr skdw hY;
hy nwnk! bRhmigAwnI sB jIvW dw mwlk hY ]8]8]
